       -------------------------------------------------------------------
       106464-1.bdf      None specifiedNone specifiedUnicodeAll languages
       8x16rk.bdf        2             2             EUC    Japanese
       jiskan16.bdf      1             1             EUC    Japanese
       hanglm16.bdf      1             2             EUC    Korean
       gb16.bdf          1             2             EUC    Chinese
       The  fourth  form of the pcfont command unloads the speci-
       fied codeset.  The display then uses the default  codeset.

